accessibility_caption: Photo by Marco de Groot • Utrecht in Depot Boijmans van Beuningen with @mvrdv, @visitnetherlands, @designboom, @gemeenterotterdam, @architecture_hunter, @boijmans, @dakendagen010, and @rotterdam_info. May be an image of nature and sky.

node.text:
Mirror, mirror, on the wall - who is the fairest one of all? 💎 Architecture-wise that must be the new art depot of @boijmans set to open this autumn.

🌳 Just look at this rooftop forest lookup! 

There will be a Grand Café with a terrace where the visitor can enjoy the view over the city. On the roof floor there is also a freely accessible exhibition space with a presentation about collecting, (the origin of) the collection, the architecture of Depot Boijmans Van Beuningen and how the depot works with the art collection; from research to conservation to restoration.

Spectacular design by @mvrdv 🥰

Don't you just #LoveRotterdam ?

See other sneak peak images and my Rotterdam favorites via #marcorama_in_rotterdam
